Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別瞎扯 快告訴我IBN5100在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…參戰了我就告訴你喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是世界改變與否的緊要關頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能因為個遊戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不參戰的話 不好意思 請回喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為女僕卻想叫主人走人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IBN5100到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.16,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不好意思 但我不會手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵喵 真有自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫你贏得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利斯炭可是全國水準的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是該對菲利斯說的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是有萬無一失的作戰計畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰代號ＧＢＡＣＫ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為Ｇ－ＢＡＣＫ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽上去挺厲害的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺有趣的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也就現在能耍耍嘴皮子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個作戰炸裂的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能會喪命也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真的吧喵 凶真
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先說好 一旦參戰 你要把知道的都告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 貓耳絕不食言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:16:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來告訴你 什麼叫做絕對無法戰勝的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由喜太失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底作戰是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道 只是凶真就像自爆一樣接連不斷的自投羅網喵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自爆…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G—BACK？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自爆？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都是冷笑話 真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 告訴我情報吧 菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:20.42,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作的好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明輸了居然還這麼神氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的可是一旦參戰就告訴我情報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 贏輸本來就是無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太記得了哎喵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 給我記住啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是頭腦派的戰略啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說是頭腦派嗎 應該是卑鄙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IBN5100在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實我還小的時候爸爸有的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經沒有了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…這難道就是在蓋亞那高原上修得的奧義
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:16:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空歡喜一場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會知道啊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是凶真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然看破了菲利斯我的through shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的僅此而已？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喵 最後見到那次是在秋葉原的神社喵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖 身在遙遠的日本給我發郵件真是謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於你的提問 去問了教授後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實IBN5100具有可以解析特殊的程式語言的機能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 電腦嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去問問爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是IBN5100
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不懂的話 就說是台古老的電腦就行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我問問看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後對一次暗語
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E…El Psy Congari
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:17:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Congroo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是牧瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧瀨？ 抱歉我沒印象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在哪見過嗎 巴黎還是倫敦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在秋葉原 剛才不還見過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼啊 原來是助手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說克莉絲蒂娜我不就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說不是蒂娜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那麼吵鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為是誰的錯啊 誰的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問這個幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下來打算去柳林神社…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 找碴嗎？ 這是找碴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的電話是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想問出你在哪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不記得有誰叫你過來過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不記得自己有被誰叫來過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我問了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 問了一下父親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親說那台電腦的確是被供獻在神社裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:18:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電腦是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是IBN5100？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這邊這位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是助手 然後IBN5100……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 你那隨便的介紹方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了我根本不是什麼助手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是為了專門介紹你而來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介紹下也用不了10秒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個麻煩的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧瀨紅莉栖 是助手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 算了 助手就助手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫漆原琉華
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾歲了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年十七歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我小一歲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧瀨小姐很成熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 你也很漂亮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那個 我去叫父親來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂無知者無慮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～沒想到真的會成為現實呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初供獻這台電腦的那個人跟我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲早會有一個需要這台電腦的年輕人出現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請好好保管
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大概是10年前的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有這種事……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是命運的巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:20.13,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(576,630)}Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運石之門的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IBN5100 Portable Computer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這個能不能借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬走了 來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是助手吧克莉絲蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是助手也不是蒂娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用推車運走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅借我們電腦 連這種事都要麻煩您…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 助手你給我注意一下狀況！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:21:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 你居然叫我注意狀況？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們關係真好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉華也要跟人家好好相處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想重複和父親一樣的失敗！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推車好像壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼非得和你落到這種地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話趕緊搬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路還長著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那挑釁一樣的態度算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.92,0:21:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 等等啊
